     H            Y.
     F** AJSR43 **********************************
     F* DELETE   AJSPP01                         *
     F* C:N.HAYAKAWA           1991.02.11        *
     F************************* COPY FROM AJSR15 *
     FAJSWP42 IP  F      14            DISK
     FAJSPL01 UF  E           K        DISK
      *
     IAJSWP42 AA  01
     I                                        1   5 SHIN1
     I                                        6  10 SHIN2
     I                                       11  12 SHIN3
     I                                       13  13 KUBUN
     I                                       14  14 KKBN
     I            DS
     I                                        1   4 J1MEK1
     I                                        1   1 MEK1
     I                                        1   2 MEK12
     I                                        2   2 MEK2
     I                                        3   3 MEK3
     I                                        4   4 MEK4
     C*
     C*ＦＡマスター削除の為のポインターセット
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           SHIN1
     C                     KFLD           SHIN2
     C                     KFLD           SHIN3
     C*
     C           KEY1      SETLLAJSPL011
     C                     SETOF                     11
     C           LOOP1     TAG
     C           KEY1      READEAJSPL011                 11
     C           *IN11     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     ELSE
     C*
     C           J1SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           J1SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     GOTO LOOP1
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           J1KDAI    IFNE KKBN
     C                     GOTO LOOP1
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDIF
     C*ファイル無しチェック
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '1'
     C                     GOTO END
     C                     END
     C*
     C*ファイル区分チェックKUBUN='*' THEN DELETE
     C*
     C                     MOVE '1'       J1MENT
     C           KUBUN     IFEQ '*'
     C                     MOVE 'D'       J1SKJY
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     J1SKYY
     C                     Z-ADDUMONTH    J1SKMM
     C                     Z-ADDUDAY      J1SKDD
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    J1KOME
     C                     MOVEL'AJSR43'  J1KOME
     C                     MOVE '0'       J1MENT
     C                     UPDATAJSPL011
     C                     END
     C*
     C*終了*
     C           END       TAG
